885
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:49,190
Once, I caught one of your men,

886
00:39:50,320 --> 00:39:52,070
thinking he was a deserter.

887
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:55,400
When I checked

888
00:39:55,400 --> 00:39:56,320
his cart,

889
00:39:57,150 --> 00:39:58,590
it was full of sky lanterns.

890
00:40:00,440 --> 00:40:01,960
I thought to myself,

891
00:40:03,110 --> 00:40:04,070
even with the battle

892
00:40:04,070 --> 00:40:05,760
so intense,

893
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:07,190
this Lu Wen

894
00:40:07,670 --> 00:40:09,590
still has the leisure

895
00:40:09,780 --> 00:40:10,920
to watch sky lanterns.

896
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:12,630
Of course.

897
00:40:13,030 --> 00:40:13,920
There's more

898
00:40:14,070 --> 00:40:15,760
to life than just

899
00:40:16,110 --> 00:40:17,360
battles and hatred.

900
00:40:19,190 --> 00:40:20,360
I fought with you

901
00:40:21,070 --> 00:40:22,920
so that those around me

902
00:40:23,070 --> 00:40:24,280
can live a peaceful and stable life,

903
00:40:25,190 --> 00:40:26,360
with feasts during festivals,

904
00:40:26,670 --> 00:40:28,840
new clothes to wear,

905
00:40:29,840 --> 00:40:30,920
and the joy of witnessing

906
00:40:31,510 --> 00:40:32,840
grand lantern displays.

907
00:40:39,360 --> 00:40:40,670
I guess.

908
00:40:45,590 --> 00:40:46,880
I know you've long been worried

909
00:40:48,510 --> 00:40:50,070
and prepared for battle,

910
00:40:51,070 --> 00:40:52,880
but I don't want you to forget

911
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:56,400
that worry and toil are not what we are after.

912
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:58,320
We should enjoy our lives.

913
00:40:59,710 --> 00:41:00,550
So,

914
00:41:02,630 --> 00:41:04,030
no matter what Prince Sui

915
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:05,510
or Three Bureaus may do,

916
00:41:06,960 --> 00:41:08,030
spending a happy holiday

917
00:41:08,440 --> 00:41:10,440
with the loved one

918
00:41:11,070 --> 00:41:12,800
is what truly matters right now.

919
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:22,080
- Take a look.
- Buns. Tasty buns.

920
00:41:22,150 --> 00:41:24,030
- These are the specialties of Xijing.
- Meat buns.

921
00:41:24,190 --> 00:41:25,280
It's all good stuff.

922
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:27,000
- It's good for you.
- Fresh steamed buns.

923
00:41:27,190 --> 00:41:28,190
I'd like a bag of walnuts.

924
00:41:28,480 --> 00:41:29,320
Okay.

925
00:41:30,230 --> 00:41:31,070
Thank you.

926
00:41:32,150 --> 00:41:34,110
- Thank you.
- Okay, take care.

927
00:41:35,590 --> 00:41:37,070
- Madam, have one of these.
- Yes, please.

928
00:41:37,360 --> 00:41:38,230
Try this.

929
00:41:38,480 --> 00:41:39,320
Thank you.

930
00:41:39,800 --> 00:41:41,280
- Is that enough?
- Thank you.

931
00:41:44,670 --> 00:41:45,510
Honey.

932
00:41:46,030 --> 00:41:46,870
Come one.

933
00:41:48,070 --> 00:41:49,630
Excuse me.

934
00:41:52,670 --> 00:41:53,880
If you want couplets,

935
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:55,550
I'll write them for you at home.

936
00:41:56,920 --> 00:41:58,030
This scholar's calligraphy

937
00:41:58,230 --> 00:41:59,760
is the finest around.

938
00:41:59,920 --> 00:42:00,840
There's no way

939
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:02,070
you can compare.

940
00:42:04,320 --> 00:42:05,400
Although it's neat,

941
00:42:05,760 --> 00:42:06,800
it's too uniform.

942
00:42:07,280 --> 00:42:08,670
The horizontal strokes lack arrangement,

943
00:42:08,670 --> 00:42:09,990
(All)
and vertical lack hidden strength.

944
00:42:10,880 --> 00:42:12,320
It's far inferior to yours.

945
00:42:13,760 --> 00:42:15,360
With such insight,

946
00:42:15,510 --> 00:42:16,510
you must

947
00:42:16,550 --> 00:42:17,440
be a good calligrapher.

948
00:42:18,030 --> 00:42:19,760
Please enlighten me, madam.

949
00:42:21,110 --> 00:42:21,950
What's the matter?

950
00:42:22,550 --> 00:42:23,390
Are you afraid?

951
00:42:24,230 --> 00:42:25,280
Enjoying lecturing others?

952
00:42:25,440 --> 00:42:26,440
That's absurd and insulting.

953
00:42:26,480 --> 00:42:27,320
Exactly.

954
00:42:28,110 --> 00:42:28,950
All right.

955
00:42:29,880 --> 00:42:30,880
Let me borrow your brush.

956
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:31,840
Please.

957
00:42:32,630 --> 00:42:33,670
Since he is curious

958
00:42:33,880 --> 00:42:35,760
about my wife's calligraphy,

959
00:42:36,030 --> 00:42:37,440
why not

960
00:42:37,590 --> 00:42:38,550
show them a little?

961
00:42:39,960 --> 00:42:40,800
Come on.

962
00:42:44,070 --> 00:42:44,910
Please.

963
00:42:50,110 --> 00:42:51,110
Writing together?

964
00:42:51,630 --> 00:42:53,230
Nothing good could come from that.

965
00:42:53,590 --> 00:42:55,510
I'm a bit selfish.

966
00:42:56,510 --> 00:42:57,960
I can't let other men

967
00:42:58,000 --> 00:43:00,400
