968
00:43:02,190 --> 00:43:03,710
Let's just write

969
00:43:04,670 --> 00:43:06,150
last year's New Year's greeting.

970
00:43:13,560 --> 00:43:16,770
♪Flowers falling by the river again♪

971
00:43:16,770 --> 00:43:17,660
(Year)

972
00:43:19,480 --> 00:43:21,000
The way you wrote it is excellent.

973
00:43:22,030 --> 00:43:23,000
Truly well done.

974
00:43:26,480 --> 00:43:29,650
♪Calm years pass by the silent bustling city♪

975
00:43:29,650 --> 00:43:32,020
♪Sitting at home♪

976
00:43:32,020 --> 00:43:36,380
(Days)

977
00:43:38,660 --> 00:43:44,640
♪If one day the river breeze blows again♪

978
00:43:45,130 --> 00:43:50,780
♪I won't be a mere reflection in the mirror♪

979
00:43:50,780 --> 00:43:55,940
(Like this)

980
00:43:56,800 --> 00:43:59,440
May each year bring us days like this.

981
00:43:59,800 --> 00:44:01,030
I'm so surprised

982
00:44:01,350 --> 00:44:03,240
- All right. Fold it.
- at how good his calligraphy is.

983
00:44:04,750 --> 00:44:08,760
♪Lies mundane dust♪

984
00:44:15,480 --> 00:44:16,320
Your calligraphy

985
00:44:16,480 --> 00:44:17,710
